+        # Check if model has make_cache (hybrid models like DeltaNet).
+        # For VLM-wrapped hybrids loaded via mlx_vlm.load on Qwen3.5/3.6,
+        # make_cache lives on `language_model`, not the outer wrapper —
+        # without this fallback, the loop below builds uniform
+        # ContiguousKVCache for every layer and DeltaNet layers receive
+        # the wrong cache type, producing fluent-looking garbage tokens.
+        # (MMLU regressed to 16.7% pre-fix; recovered to 93.0% with it.)
