+            # Replace ONLY plain KVCache (full attention) with our
+            # quantized ContiguousKVCache. Keep RotatingKVCache NATIVE —
+            # its rotating-ring-buffer semantics are load-bearing for
+            # sliding-attention layers (Gemma 4 sliding_window=1024).
+            # Replacing it with non-rotating ContiguousKVCache means
